rComments: Very inspiring and organized lectures. The class is very casual and entertaining, and the assignment is fun to do. Highly recommended!
Wonderful studio instructor. So caring, kind and empathetic.
relaxed, casual class. very organized and clear lectures. really fun class as far as architectural theory goes. can be very generous with marking. highly recommend enrolling in any course he teaches.
Love him! Very well organized and communicated the course material exceptionally well. Readings were interesting!
amazing prof. Best one in school. Young, exciting, intelligent, inspiring,hardworking. You can tell he loves what he does and architecture.

i highly commend his approach in teaching this course. he kept it enticing and fun, he always introduced sth new and uptodate to counter the historical theory aspects of the course.  the readings were fair and interesting. the tests sometimes were too much on memory of minor details rather than the big picture. nevertheless, good course.
